Open Source FPV Frame Version 1
The SOURCE AUREO is an ultralight 7" frame,
made for pilots who crave for range. Made with a rohacell
like material sandwiched between 2 layers of carbon,
the result is a super lightweight 7" frame - @49.5g.
It fits and protects all the up-to-date components and is optimized for range.
The SOURCE AUREO is your perfect long range cruiser,
and is recommended for pro pilots only.
The frame is donated to the community to empower creators
and makers, and integrate best practices and current trends
faster into a continuously manufactured product. In return, it
allows the local distribution network to have cheap and direct
access to a good frame in order to allow them TO compete in
an increasingly predatory marketplace.
